Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.40,0:00:21.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}坚强的内心充满推理的能量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.20,0:00:22.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}永远以最敏锐的节奏揭开案情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.90,0:00:24.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}终于要公开帽子下的内容了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.90,0:00:26.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}目暮警官很酷的过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.80,0:00:28.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.40,0:00:30.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}看上去是小孩 头脑却是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.30,0:00:32.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}他的名字就是名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.40,0:01:45.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}被园子一起叫去商场买东西的我们几个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.30,0:01:53.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但叔叔却意外的卷入目暮警官的调查中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.10,0:01:58.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}警官他们正在调查妇女连续被殴打的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.10,0:02:00.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就在这时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.20,0:02:03.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}兰在商场的停车场内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.30,0:02:04.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}发现了第四个受害者的尸体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.30,0:02:16.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}目暮警官等人继续调查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.00,0:02:19.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}但目暮警官的样子却有点不对劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.60,0:02:25.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}警官 请你再让我们在这里检查一会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.20,0:02:26.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}应该还可以找到什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.00,0:02:28.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}而且我感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.40,0:02:31.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}犯人现在应该还在这附近才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.60,0:02:33.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那就随便你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.20,0:02:37.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}目暮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.70,0:02:43.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你该不会是还在意当年的那件案子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.10,0:02:50.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}藏在你那顶帽子下被封印了的案子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.10,0:02:57.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}被封印的目暮的秘密(后编)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.90,0:03:15.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那 叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.40,0:03:17.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}车钥匙借我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.10,0:03:19.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}我看还得在这里待上一阵子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.80,0:03:21.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}想把东西放到车上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.40,0:03:23.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}先到百货公司去上一下洗手间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.30,0:03:25.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}那你动作得快一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.50,0:03:27.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}百货公司应该快要关门了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.50,0:03:29.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.30,0:03:30.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k80}那你顺便帮我放吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.80,0:03:31.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.30,0:03:40.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}找到了 就是这辆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.40,0:03:43.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}旁边这辆车是怎么停的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.00,0:03:45.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}停的靠我们这么近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.80,0:03:48.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}车门根本就打不开了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.70,0:04:02.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}警官 我已经去确认过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.60,0:04:03.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.80,0:04:05.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}没错 第二位受害者也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.40,0:04:08.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}从自己开的车下来之后才到公园上厕所的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.20,0:04:10.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.80,0:04:12.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}但我还是不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.20,0:04:14.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}歹徒为何针对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.60,0:04:16.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}自己开车又打扮新潮的女孩子下手呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.40,0:04:19.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}难道说这其中另有什么原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.50,0:04:22.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}她们四人还有什么共同点是我们没发现的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.80,0:04:25.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.00,0:04:27.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}这里也在清理啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.50,0:04:31.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}要清理不会等关了门之后再清理吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.10,0:04:34.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}下一个洗手间要走到八楼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.40,0:04:38.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎么我连上厕所都这么不顺利啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.70,0:04:41.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}今天非常感谢各位顾客光临本百货公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.00,0:04:44.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}马上就到了本馆关门的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.40,0:04:46.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}欢迎各位有机会再次光临本馆购物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.90,0:04:48.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}不会吧 要关门了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.50,0:04:50.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}我们把尸体搬走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.20,0:04:51.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.40,0:05:01.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}她的鞋子掉下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.90,0:05:02.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.70,0:05:06.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.40,0:05:08.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k70}这只鞋子怎么穿不上啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.50,0:05:11.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}兰姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.60,0:05:14.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}你刚才不是说有什么地方怪怪的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.80,0:05:16.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}该不会是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.70,0:05:20.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}没错没错 就是这点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.80,0:05:22.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}现在化了黑人妆的女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.90,0:05:24.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}是不会穿成那样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.70,0:05:27.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}这么说来 难道歹徒会是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.10,0:05:38.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.90,0:05:42.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k80}先别关灯 我还里面啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.90,0:05:47.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}等等 没有人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.70,0:05:53.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.80,0:05:55.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}厚底鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.20,0:05:58.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}在这个停车场里被杀害的蓝泽小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.70,0:06:02.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}其实脚下穿的原本应该是一双厚底鞋是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.30,0:06:05.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因为现在会化黑人妆的女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.80,0:06:08.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}一般来说是不会穿平底的普通鞋的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.10,0:06:10.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是吧 兰姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.20,0:06:14.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.40,0:06:18.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}歹徒为什么要刻意把被害人的鞋子换掉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.50,0:06:20.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我想 他一定是不想被人发现这点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.40,0:06:23.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}因为他攻击的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.20,0:06:26.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}全都是穿厚底鞋开车的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.90,0:06:27.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.60,0:06:30.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}说回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.50,0:06:33.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k90}现在想想其他三位小姐遭到攻击的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.90,0:06:36.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}脸上也的确都化了夸张的黑人妆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.60,0:06:38.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}这么说 这三名受害者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.50,0:06:39.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}在被攻击的当时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.50,0:06:42.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}穿着厚底鞋的可能性应该也很高了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.40,0:06:42.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.70,0:06:45.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}我记得由美曾经跟我说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.70,0:06:47.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}蓝泽小姐一年前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.60,0:06:49.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}在这个停车场引发的那场交通意外 最大的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.30,0:06:54.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}就是因为她脚上穿了一双厚底鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.40,0:06:56.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}减低了刹车的敏感度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.70,0:06:58.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}所以才会引发那场悲剧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.70,0:07:00.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}那是真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.60,0:07:01.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.40,0:07:04.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k80}在那场车祸中丧生的少年早就离婚的父母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.80,0:07:07.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}当时非常坚定肇事是因为这个原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.00,0:07:09.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}结果却没有得到法官的认同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.30,0:07:11.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}他的父母早就离婚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.50,0:07:15.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}对 听说主要原因是因为他酗酒才离婚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.90,0:07:16.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我还记得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.40,0:07:19.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}这名离婚的父亲好象叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.90,0:07:21.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}这个人应该姓“定金”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.40,0:07:24.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}没错 就是姓定金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.10,0:07:30.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}等等 刚才那位警卫好像也姓定金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.70,0:07:35.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}难道说这件案子的歹徒就是那个警卫吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.80,0:07:39.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}高木老弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.80,0:07:41.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}你立刻去查清楚一年前那场车祸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.90,0:07:42.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.90,0:07:45.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}你们现在立刻去查出定金警卫的下落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.70,0:07:46.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.70,0:07:49.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}不过 你怎么会知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.10,0:07:51.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}其实这很简单啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.20,0:07:54.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}因为这名歹徒攻击的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.60,0:07:57.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}全都是穿了厚底鞋自己开车的女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.10,0:08:00.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这点从车子外面根本就看不出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.90,0:08:04.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}而且遭到攻击的又全是这家百货公司的顾客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.60,0:08:05.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.30,0:08:06.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k70}我才会觉得一直在地下停车场里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.90,0:08:12.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}看顾客上下车的警卫最可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.60,0:08:13.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.50,0:08:17.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k90}那名歹徒的身高在150公分上下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.20,0:08:19.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}有两名被害者都指称
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.30,0:08:23.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}而那名警卫说他的身高是167公分 这怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.40,0:08:26.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}叔叔你又故意装傻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.90,0:08:28.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}那些遭到攻击的姐姐这么说只不过是想表达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.90,0:08:33.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}她们认为歹徒的身高跟自己差不多罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.20,0:08:34.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}既然她们在案发当时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.10,0:08:37.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k90}脚上都穿了一双超过10公分的厚底鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.30,0:08:40.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就表示歹徒的身高最少应该再加上10公分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.60,0:08:42.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}叔叔根本就是在明知故问嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.90,0:08:44.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.30,0:08:47.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}我们是在那几个女孩到总局侦讯的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.50,0:08:48.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}替她们量的身高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.40,0:08:51.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}当时因为她们是来录口供的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.50,0:08:53.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}所以才没有穿那么夸张的厚底鞋来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.70,0:08:55.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.60,0:08:57.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k90}如果歹徒想报复蓝泽小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.90,0:08:59.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}他就不用埋伏在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.90,0:09:02.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}可以直接到她家找她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.00,0:09:03.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}难道你忘了吗 毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.70,0:09:06.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}这名死者今年才20岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.30,0:09:09.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}一年前那场车祸发生的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.70,0:09:11.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}她应该还未成年才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.30,0:09:14.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}警方不会发表未成年嫌疑犯的住址
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.80,0:09:17.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因此歹徒也只能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.90,0:09:19.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}在自己儿子被撞的这个停车场耐心等候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.90,0:09:24.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}因为他相信这个女孩一定会再来这个百货公司的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.90,0:09:28.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是她始终没有出现 把他的耐性全磨光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.00,0:09:29.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}才会转而迁怒那些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.60,0:09:32.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}穿了厚底鞋又自己开车来的女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.20,0:09:33.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}接连的下手攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.70,0:09:41.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}警官 我已经查明整个案件了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.10,0:09:43.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}那个警卫果然就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.80,0:09:46.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}一年前在车祸中丧生的那名少年的父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.10,0:09:49.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那你说 他现在在什么地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.20,0:09:49.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.00,0:09:52.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k80}我在停车场里找到了他的车子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.90,0:09:54.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}但是都没有看到他的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.20,0:09:59.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎么了 兰姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.30,0:10:02.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}园子怎么还没有回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.60,0:10:06.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}她说把东西放到车上后去一下洗手间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.90,0:10:08.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}把东西放到车上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.50,0:10:11.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}我记得她穿的鞋子也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.60,0:10:18.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.10,0:10:20.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}小兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.60,0:10:23.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}现在 我还在百货公司里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.80,0:10:27.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我再告诉你更夸张的 实在是太过分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.30,0:10:30.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}刚才 我在洗手间里是多坐了一会儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.20,0:10:31.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}可是他们也用不着这么快就关灯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.80,0:10:51.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎么 你笑什么 园子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.30,0:10:53.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.70,0:10:56.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}我只是觉得有点不大对劲而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.90,0:11:25.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}被看到了 被看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.20,0:11:27.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}我的脸被看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.90,0:11:31.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}园子 你说话啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.50,0:11:33.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}他一定是弄错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.50,0:11:36.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}歹徒一定是看到园子姐姐刚才拿着车钥匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.50,0:11:37.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}把东西放到车上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.70,0:11:41.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}就认为她也是一个穿了厚底鞋自己开车的女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.30,0:11:42.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.20,0:11:45.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}她刚才说她在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.10,0:11:46.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}她还在百货公司里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.20,0:11:48.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}电话是不是被切断了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.00,0:11:50.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}电话还没有被切断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.20,0:11:53.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}我只是听到远方有机器微微作响的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.40,0:11:55.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}机器的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.90,0:11:58.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}请您选择一个喜欢的外框
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.20,0:12:01.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}摆好姿势之后就可以按按钮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.00,0:12:04.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是照大头贴的机器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.60,0:12:06.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}这家百货公司有大头贴机器吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.20,0:12:08.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.90,0:12:09.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}我记得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.90,0:12:12.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}10楼的餐饮街旁边的楼梯间里有两台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.00,0:12:15.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}对了 下面的楼层虽然关门了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.00,0:12:17.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但餐厅通常营业得比较晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.20,0:12:21.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}我想园子一定是想从那里的电梯坐到楼下去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.00,0:12:24.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那么高木去把百货公司的照明打开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.80,0:12:27.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}目暮与佐藤搭电梯从上往下搜索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.90,0:12:29.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}其他人由下向上搜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.50,0:12:30.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}保护那名少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.70,0:12:32.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}一定要抓到这名歹徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.50,0:12:33.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.20,0:12:37.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}请大家让一下路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.70,0:12:41.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}目暮警官还真是干劲十足呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.20,0:12:43.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因为这次太像了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.40,0:12:48.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}这一次的事情与他第一件办的案子实在太像了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.80,0:12:54.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}对了 你女儿和那个戴眼镜的小鬼跑哪里去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.10,0:13:33.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.50,0:13:37.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.50,0:13:39.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}错不了 这的确是园子的手机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.60,0:13:43.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}餐饮街的客人都表示没有看到他们两个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.70,0:13:46.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}园子应该是跑到百货公司里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.70,0:13:49.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}高木 你们还没找到人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.80,0:13:56.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你们都是一群恶魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.10,0:14:00.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}你们都是装出一副清纯的模样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.60,0:14:03.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}犯罪不眨眼的小恶魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.60,0:14:06.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是恶魔就没有活下去的价值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.50,0:14:12.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}停电了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.50,0:14:14.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}该死 偏偏挑在这个时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.40,0:14:21.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}园子 园子你在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.60,0:14:23.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}园子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.90,0:14:25.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}先安静一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.20,0:14:31.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这是什么东西散落在地上的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.70,0:14:33.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}是沙子 白米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.60,0:14:35.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}不对 应该再大一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.20,0:14:38.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}会不会是铺放在水族箱的小石头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.90,0:14:40.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}宠物专柜在四楼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.80,0:14:42.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}那她应该就在四楼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.60,0:14:43.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.80,0:15:05.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.40,0:15:10.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}其实我只是想给你点教训罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.50,0:15:17.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但你看到了我的脸 就休想活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.50,0:15:23.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}园子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.70,0:15:24.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}园子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.10,0:15:28.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}真是怪了 宠物专柜根本就没有人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.40,0:15:29.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}园子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.20,0:15:33.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}这就怪了 根本就没有破坏或是散落的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.40,0:15:36.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}难道说 刚才的那个声音是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.00,0:15:40.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}怪就怪你不该看到我的脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.00,0:15:57.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.00,0:16:05.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎么样 这感觉好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.40,0:16:13.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我问你伤害了别人你的心里好过了点吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.40,0:16:18.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我知道你是想对开车技术不好的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.70,0:16:21.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}用这根正义的铁锤执行正义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.90,0:16:22.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是很不幸的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.50,0:16:24.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k60}这孩子只是将东西放到车上而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.90,0:16:26.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}她根本高中都还没毕业
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.60,0:16:31.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你的这种行为根本不是在伸张正义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.70,0:16:34.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}也不是为了你那死去的儿子报仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.40,0:16:36.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}你只不过是迁怒罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.40,0:16:41.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这全是你独断独行 玩弄人命于股掌之间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.10,0:16:44.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}毫无意义可言的发泄行为罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.10,0:16:47.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你到现在还不懂吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.60,0:17:02.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}其实我只是想让那个女孩向我道歉罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.90,0:17:04.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我要她改穿规矩的鞋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.40,0:17:07.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}对我在天国的儿子道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.10,0:17:10.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}好告慰他的在天之灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.50,0:17:15.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我一开始真的只有这个念头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.30,0:17:17.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.90,0:17:30.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}园子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.20,0:17:34.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}小兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.70,0:17:35.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k50}兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.70,0:17:37.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不要紧没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.00,0:17:39.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}好可怕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.70,0:17:43.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}警官 你怎么知道是在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.60,0:17:44.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}这没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.10,0:17:47.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}我只是自然的被引到这里罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.20,0:17:50.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}使这些石子引我来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.10,0:17:54.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}警官 你不要紧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.60,0:17:56.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}放心 这没有什么大碍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.00,0:17:59.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}只是过去的那个旧伤裂了口而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.70,0:18:03.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}是我没处理好过去留下的一道旧伤口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.20,0:19:35.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.30,0:19:38.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}那是他过去的案子留下的旧伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.30,0:19:43.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}对 目暮就是为了掩饰他头上的那道疤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.20,0:19:45.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}才会走到哪里都戴着那顶帽子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.10,0:19:48.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}可是 对刑警来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.10,0:19:50.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}在执勤的时候负伤就等于勋章一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.00,0:19:53.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}他根本就不需要藏起来嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.10,0:19:55.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}那到疤已经有20年了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.00,0:19:56.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}我记得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.60,0:20:00.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k60}那还是在目暮刚当上刑警的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.40,0:20:04.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你也应该听过才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.20,0:20:07.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}就是连续开车撞高中女生逃逸的那件案子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.80,0:20:09.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}听过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.60,0:20:15.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}嫌疑犯行凶的动机是受到不良高中女生的恐吓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.80,0:20:16.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他一般都会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.80,0:20:20.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}看准了这些高中女生落单的时候才开车追撞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.50,0:20:22.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}做法非常卑劣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.00,0:20:26.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}当年在不良少女群体之间非常流行一种订做制服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.50,0:20:30.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}将褶裙可以拉长的穿法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.00,0:20:31.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}却因此成了他的目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.90,0:20:36.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}一开始他在撞了人之后就会逃逸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.10,0:20:41.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但几次之后他只要不把被害者撞死就不会罢休
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.40,0:20:45.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因此我们警方只有警告附近的高中女生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.80,0:20:48.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}千万别再穿那种裙子到外面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.60,0:20:51.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}的确就没有同样的悲剧发生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.20,0:20:54.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这个时候 有个高中女生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.80,0:20:57.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}表示她愿意负责将歹徒引诱出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.80,0:21:00.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}还说这么做是为了替她死去的朋友报仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.60,0:21:03.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我们自然是加以阻止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.60,0:21:05.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}但是那名女孩对警方向来非常反感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.10,0:21:07.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}根本不顾我们的阻止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.70,0:21:08.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}在无奈之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.80,0:21:12.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}我们才特别派目暮保护那名学生的安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.20,0:21:31.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是嫌疑犯却想把她和目暮一起撞死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.00,0:21:34.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}还好目暮记下了那辆车的车号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.90,0:21:36.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}终于将嫌疑犯逮捕到案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.80,0:21:39.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}但是代价却太大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.20,0:21:43.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}目暮还好 只是头上受了一处重伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.80,0:21:46.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那位高中女生的头部与身体却遭到猛烈撞击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.90,0:21:51.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}在我们赶到的时候就看到她浑身是血倒在地上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.90,0:21:58.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那么 目暮警官他不脱那顶帽子就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.20,0:22:00.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你说得没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.70,0:22:02.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}不管谁看到他头上那么大的疤痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.40,0:22:05.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}一定会询问他伤势的由来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.00,0:22:07.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这么一来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.40,0:22:09.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}就逼得他必须要重新回想起当年那件案子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.30,0:22:12.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以目暮呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.60,0:22:15.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}才会用那顶帽子遮住他的伤口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.10,0:22:19.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}毕竟那道疤痕代表了一段痛苦的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.20,0:22:25.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以目暮警官才会那么反对引诱歹徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.00,0:22:28.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因为他不希望再有人像那个女孩一样牺牲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.50,0:22:30.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}拜托
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.60,0:22:33.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}她的头部与身体虽然受了重伤没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.40,0:22:34.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}但她没有死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.40,0:22:38.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}她后来还成了目暮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.20,0:22:40.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}松本警政厅长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.50,0:22:43.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你一定是来医院探病的对不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.60,0:22:45.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你来得正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.40,0:22:49.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k80}高木警官跟白鸟警官几分钟前才刚刚回去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.50,0:22:52.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他们两个也都来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.50,0:22:56.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是啊 他们说毕竟是工作上的伙伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.30,0:22:59.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}她的额头上有道疤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.80,0:23:00.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}难道说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.90,0:23:02.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}小碧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.40,0:23:04.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}快来帮我削苹果啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.10,0:23:09.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}年纪这么大了还是喜欢撒娇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.30,0:23:12.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}看来 我得快点让他开始工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.00,0:23:13.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}他才会有点活力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.20,0:23:16.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}是啊 到时候还要麻烦您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.50,0:23:19.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我想到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.20,0:23:21.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k70}听说目暮警官的老婆小碧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.50,0:23:24.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}过去好像也曾经荒唐过一阵子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.80,0:23:26.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这么说来的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.00,0:23:28.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}目暮警官之所以不把帽子脱掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.60,0:23:30.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}是因为他不希望别人看到之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.60,0:23:33.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}就取笑他与他老婆认识的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.10,0:23:39.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}还没有好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.30,0:23:48.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}由我和那家伙来一起揭开21世纪的序幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.30,0:23:51.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}新一的推理和基德的魔术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.30,0:23:52.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}宿命对决的120分钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.30,0:23:54.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}光辉的延续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.30,0:23:56.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}名侦探柯南2001特别节目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.40,0:23:59.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}2001年1月8日周一晚放送
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.70,0:24:02.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.10,0:24:04.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}10元硬币
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.00,0:24:07.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}下一回是2001年的2小时特别篇 是1月8日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.30,0:24:08.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}是1月8日1月8日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.50,0:24:09.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}是1月8日
